       That's the goal... just to simplify things really.<br /><br />I was thinking about configuration files (NTS export file, Samba config, etc) and think it might be a good idea to keep a backup of the configuration files on the main harddrive so they can be copied back rather than having to be manually editted.<br /><br />** ok I can edit this one. I'll upload the script to pastebin when I've got one that vaguely works! **<br /><br />Mark
